>TACTICAL ARSENAL</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover a diverse range of firearms, each with distinct advantages and drawbacks. </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Swap on the fly:</strong> Adapt to the situation instantly.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Experiment:</strong> Find unique weapon combinations to conquer difficult enemy types.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2737680/extras/09968bda10b223e6425d56ef58607ee9.poster.avif?t=1774164097\" width=800 height=422 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2737680/extras/09968bda10b223e6425d56ef58607ee9.webm?t=1774164097\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2737680/extras/09968bda10b223e6425d56ef58607ee9.mp4?t=1774164097\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ARENA GATING</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every cavern is an arena. When you enter a new zone, the exits seal shut. You must <strong>clear the room</strong> of all hostiles to unlock the path forward. There is no running away—only fighting through.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EXPLORE & EVOLVE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find helpful pick-ups to aid your journey. Utilise <strong>Portals</strong> to bank your items and backtrack to recover loot you left behind.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2737680/extras/5b78c3ceefdd294b48f7b42452e8091b.poster.avif?t=1774164097\" width=800 height=444 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.co